text: DisoBAYish is the fifth studio album by rapper Messy Marv, released on March 9, 2004. Guest appearances on the album include Yukmouth, E-40, Too Short, and Nate Dogg. It peaked at number 76 on the Billboard Top R&B;/Hip-Hop Albums, and number 49 on the Billboard Top Independent Albums.[ ((( Disobayish > Charts & Awards > Billboard Albums )))].
